_sText:
Fy_gow_gridlock is a map based on the multiplayer map on Gears of War.

This map is currently in Beta stage!

Updates in detail will be made for the final!

I am aware of a bug within the map that includes texture bugs, but thats only in a few areas.

Everything is sized in a way so it closely matches the actual map.

Please give some comments and some advice.Even Assess if you wish.

Most of all, are bugs and any improvements.

I will be trying to add some scenery buildings outside the map for the final.

Thanks and Enjoy.

( It works well with the 5 vs 5 like in Gears of War ;) )

THE FINAL VERSION IS RELEASED - http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/56525
